      <talk_question mid="40"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>Then, you'd best get going. I'm extremely busy, you know.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n3049_hiver_grave-3" image="QN_TombStone01.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
