      <talk_question mid="41"><![CDATA[<html>$Hiver's Grave$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(I remember this simply being a mound in the sand…</FONT><FONT color=#7e12d2>Now it's a proper grave</FONT><BR>
<FONT color=#7e12d2>with a tombstone.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n3049_hiver_grave-3-a" image="QN_Hiver.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n3049_hiver_grave-3-b" mid="122" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html><FONT color=#7e12d2>(You place the dagger and clothing beside the device.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="42"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(After barely digging, you hit something small and hard.<BR>Dusting off the dirt reveals it to be a music playing device.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
