      <talk_question mid="43"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(You cover the items with soil and flatten the ground to complete the grave.)</FONT><FONT color=#662500><BR>There's only one thing left now.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
