      <talk_question mid="45"><![CDATA[<html>$Brother and Sister's Tomb$<BR>A cold breeze blows through the <FONT color=#086171>Blue Wind Plains</FONT>.<BR>It's as if you can hear a faint song in the wind.<BR>And the laughter of a brother and sister.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2091_refugee_girl-5" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2091_refugee_girl-5-a" mid="127" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Is that Hiver's song?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="46"><![CDATA[<html>$Refugee Girl$<BR><FONT color=#a94407>I have nothing. Nothing to eat, and nothing to wear.<BR>Nothing to lose, so I have nothing to fear. Nothing to leave behind when I die.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2091_refugee_girl-5-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2091_refugee_girl-5-b" mid="128" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Hey… How do you know that song…?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="47"><![CDATA[<html>$Refugee Girl$<BR><FONT color=#a94407>And nothing to be remembered for when I die.<BR>Nothing to be remembered for when I die...</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2091_refugee_girl-5-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2091_refugee_girl-5-c" mid="129" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Do you know me?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="48"><![CDATA[<html>$Refugee Girl$<BR>Oh, adventurer! Hello. Have you been well?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2091_refugee_girl-5-c" image="QN_Child_Grele.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2091_refugee_girl-5-d" mid="130" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Oh… the crying girl who lost her grandfather…)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n2091_refugee_girl-5-d" mid="131" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Right. You came to Merca?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="49"><![CDATA[<html>$Refugee Girl$<BR>Of course. You saved me after I came to <FONT color=#086171>Rhadames</FONT> with Grandpa…<BR>You and a <FONT color=#a82424>sort of scary-looking guy</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2091_refugee_girl-5-d" image="QN_Soceressanna.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2091_refugee_girl-5-e" mid="132" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>That's good. But that song… Where did you learn it?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="50"><![CDATA[<html>$Refugee Girl$<BR>Yes. After arriving in <FONT color=#086171>Rhadames</FONT>, I spent some time with <FONT color=#a82424>Sorceress Anna</FONT>.<BR>But I came here because I heard there was someone who would take care of me and that it was safe here.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2091_refugee_girl-5-e" image="QN_Hiver.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2091_refugee_girl-5-f" mid="133" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Ah, I see.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="51"><![CDATA[<html>$Refugee Girl$<BR>Song? I don't know, it seemed like everyone sang it. They said singing it would put my mind at ease.<BR>It really worked. It's a marvelous song.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2091_refugee_girl-5-f" image="QN_Grele.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2091_refugee_girl-5-g" mid="134" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Okay...</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="52"><![CDATA[<html>$Refugee Girl$<BR>And, I still want to return to my hometown with everyone, but... it's not going to happen.<BR>So please give my regards to <FONT color=#a82424>that guy</FONT> too. And tell him I'm doing well…</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2091_refugee_girl-5-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2091_refugee_girl-5-h" mid="136" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>No, I'd be happy to give him your message. Well, take care.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="135"><![CDATA[<html>$Refugee Girl$<BR>
Oh? Are you okay? Your complexion is a bit…<BR>
Are you ill? Is everything okay?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2091_refugee_girl-5-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2091_refugee_girl-5-i" mid="138" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Bids the girl farewell.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="137"><![CDATA[<html>$Refugee Girl$<BR>
<FONT color=#7e12d2>(The girl smiles timidly.)</FONT><BR>
That's good. So long!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
