         <title mid="53"><![CDATA[Their Last Home]]></title>
         <contents mid="54"><![CDATA[<html>According to Vandar, <FONT color=#a82424>Grele</FONT> seemed like he wanted to ask a favor related to the <FONT color=#086171>Blue Wind Plains</FONT>. Grele said he made a <FONT color=#086171>grave for Hiver</FONT> there before… Perhaps he wanted to be buried there with her? You should discuss the matter further with <FONT color=#a82424>Sorceress Anna</FONT>.<BR><BR>
<FONT color=#086171>Rhadames</FONT> - <FONT color=#a82424>Sorceress Anna</FONT></html>]]></contents>
