         <title mid="57"><![CDATA[His Apology]]></title>
         <contents mid="58"><![CDATA[<html>After describing Shalica's condition, Sorceress Anna hands over the belongings of <FONT color=#a82424>Grele and Hiver</FONT>. You thought of someone else who would be interested in hearing Shalica's condition before you head to <FONT color=#086171>Blue Wind Plains</FONT>. You should go there and pass on the news.<BR>
<BR><FONT color=#086171> Merca's Heart  </FONT>- <FONT color=#a82424> President Vernicka </FONT></html>]]></contents>
         <destination mid="59"><![CDATA[Talk to President Vernicka in Merca’s Headquarters.]]></destination>
         <todo_msg mid="60"><![CDATA[Speak with President Vernicka at Merca’s Headquarters.]]></todo_msg>
