         <title mid="61"><![CDATA[One Last Farewell]]></title>
         <contents mid="62"><![CDATA[<html>You went to give <FONT color=#a82424>President Vernicka</FONT> the news about Shalica and he gave you an <FONT color=#a82424>Ice Flower</FONT>, saying it was his way of apologizing to Grele. You should now head to the <FONT color=#086171>Blue Wind Plains</FONT>.<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>※ You cannot do this quest while in a party.<BR><BR></FONT><FONT color=#086171>Merca (Blue Sand Trade Route)</FONT><FONT color=#2b2723> → </FONT><FONT color=#a82424>Blue Wind Plains (Hiver's Grave)</FONT></html>]]></contents>
         <destination mid="63"><![CDATA[(Solo) Bury the belongings of the siblings in the Blue Wind Plains]]></destination>
